import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { FoodBoxService } from '../food-box.service'; import { FormBuilder, FormControl, FormGroup, Validators } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-review', templateUrl: './review.component.html', styleUrls: ['./review.component.css'] }) export class ReviewComponent implements OnInit { reviewUserName = ''; reviewlist: any[]; addReviewItem: FormGroup; constructor(private service: FoodBoxService, private rev: FormBuilder) {} ngOnInit(): void { let response = this.service.getReviews(); response.subscribe((data: any) => (this.reviewlist = data)); this.service.getUserByEmail(sessionStorage.getItem('userSession')).subscribe( (user) => { this.reviewUserName = user.name; this.initializeForm(); } ); } initializeForm(): void { this.addReviewItem = this.rev.group({ reviewUserName: new FormControl({ value: this.reviewUserName, disabled: true }, [Validators.required]), reviewComment: new FormControl('', [Validators.required]), reviewStar: new FormControl('', [Validators.required]) }); } getArray(count: number): any[] { return new Array(count); } message: any; submitReview(): void { console.log(this.addReviewItem.value); let response = this.service.addReview(this.addReviewItem.value); response.subscribe((data: any) => { this.message = data; this.addReviewItem.reset(); }); } }
